thread.title: BRIEF-Vanfund Urban Investment and Development updates on stake sale and acquisition

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Vanfund Urban Investment and Development updates on stake sale and acquisition

organizations.name: vanfund urban investment and development co ltd

text:
Jan 25(Reuters) - Vanfund Urban Investment and Development Co Ltd
* Says it sells 90 percent stake in Suifenhe-based trading firm and acquires 60 percent stake in Chengdu-based medical science and technology development firm
* Says it scraps plan to acquire 100 percent stake in a Sichuan-based network firm
* Previous news was disclosed on Jan. 20, 2017
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/XzeWFD
